Package com.thelocalmarketplace.hardware

Class CoinTray

java.lang.Object
com.tdc.AbstractComponent<IComponentObserver>
com.thelocalmarketplace.hardware.CoinTray
All Implemented Interfaces:
IComponent<IComponentObserver>, Sink<Coin>
public class CoinTray extends AbstractComponent<IComponentObserver> implements Sink<Coin>
Simulates the tray where dispensed coins go for the user to collect them. It is a passive device requiring no power, being gravity-fed.
